{"tid":240973,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"那些<銀魂>教會我們的事","createTime":"2017-05-12T19:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T13:27:04.000Z","uid":71379,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e61ca763377c0df4c0225184512b61e22c03296","tid":240973,"uid":71379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:39:37.000Z","msg":"見銀魂就嚟埋尾<br />\n小弟特登重睇一次<br />\n再一次感受到銀魂係幾咁完美<br />\n揉合史實、惡搞、道理、笑料、感動位、打鬥<br />\n故事連貫、一致<br />\n角色設定飽滿、每個人有各自特性同背景故事去配合/觸發相應劇情<br />\n仲要係小數作畫由開始就不過不失，畫到最後仲明顯見到升咗幾個級數<br />\n<br />\n今次重睇順手CAP低啲好值得深思嘅對白開心SHARE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望令多啲巴打可以接觸到銀魂，唔好浪費一套咁好嘅漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0cMNrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0cMNrn.jpg&h=4e8a44b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/033605_54a23527799443fe4c0bc9bc6dfe1478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F033605_54a23527799443fe4c0bc9bc6dfe1478.jpg&h=bd36cd95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7s8SFoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7s8SFoP.jpg&h=2aba7b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TiA9HU5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTiA9HU5.jpg&h=621bb09a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/033613_dcd3f145ddf188deb55dd6f2f0f1dd26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F033613_dcd3f145ddf188deb55dd6f2f0f1dd26.jpg&h=4981b6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/033718_8813047ec34a1c7e2b1177898f6c6d6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F033718_8813047ec34a1c7e2b1177898f6c6d6f.jpg&h=ea2b3b32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2652t5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2652t5.jpg&h=8bfb46c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/033721_754834b30a40975b59f91d9eaf041f67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F033721_754834b30a40975b59f91d9eaf041f67.jpg&h=2b9ef054&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1539k8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1539k8.jpg&h=6d4ea6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/033724_074e10d69abb5eb938d2c64f77918bf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F033724_074e10d69abb5eb938d2c64f77918bf2.jpg&h=6ea1ad62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/033824_ef73ab67938fbc4979255836f5bd11e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F033824_ef73ab67938fbc4979255836f5bd11e7.jpg&h=3e00f0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/321A417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F321A417.jpg&h=aa3c9d20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9X56L8h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9X56L8h.jpg&h=5d831591&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/033830_a173776fb0dea41ccda9d38329d10769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F033830_a173776fb0dea41ccda9d38329d10769.jpg&h=c987d859&s={SIZE}\