ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6640bb3c68e01391f08c5d6844e8308ed433420","tid":240973,"uid":64193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:42:01.000Z","msg":"阿銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216fc3a4bfadf1a328ebab23f9fe03ce04c1772d","tid":240973,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:44:32.000Z","msg":"漫畫神威岩岩出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空知用左咁多篇幅講高衫 <br />\n希望可以完整d洗白神威 打輸左就改邪歸正好突兀"},{"pid":"6f2d27826f1b8ab650864910b2caf923f8370783","tid":240973,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:45:18.000Z","msg":"樓主嗰啲圖唔係銀魂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/034450_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F034450_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=a2ea1136&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e7e84a05dca1e822bdd53b50522d31d24ec9140","tid":240973,"uid":71379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>漫畫神威岩岩出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空知用左咁多篇幅講高衫 <br />\n希望可以完整d洗白神威 打輸左就改邪歸正好突兀</blockquote><br />\n其實都打咗好多鑊先洗得白<br />\n銀魂嘅洗白方式屈機在所有「壞人」都唔係純粹地壞 <br />\n只係一直堅持住一啲錯嘅嘢、用錯嘅方式去實踐一啲嘢<br />\n但其實好多時只係鑽牛角尖"},{"pid":"7f828c4b7c101a7a9c89d438f50061803a847b5a","tid":240973,"uid":392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:47:43.000Z","msg":"銀魂跟其他少年漫都不同的地方在於：其他的少年漫都是在講如何追逐夢想，而銀魂則是在告訴你夢想破滅之後如何生活"},{"pid":"dbb3504fabd8bad056f7d738a33e761841a68b48","tid":240973,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T20:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>銀魂跟其他少年漫都不同的地方在於：其他的少年漫都是在講如何追逐夢想，而銀魂則是在告訴你夢想破滅之後如何生活</blockquote><br />\n因為佢地係男仔 阿銀先係男人"},{"pid":"cd6120b088d2392393643a680ea3377df6ca8e93","tid":240973,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T20:30:41.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b694798a73ebf8ed23247eb7055b46892cbbba","tid":240973,"uid":85909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T21:25:56.000Z","msg":"有一話係攞番簡泡黎講人生/夢想，唔太記得<br />\n果陣睇完之一係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69630b6ec615326085f031ed76d3222c8d94d6fa","tid":240973,"uid":85909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T21:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一話係攞番簡泡黎講人生/夢想，唔太記得<br />\n果陣睇完之<span style=\"color: red;\">後</span>係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"edff2338d4b2363c4ff9a12337144dc560ba52d1","tid":240973,"uid":11913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2e694bb627eb8fc2194ea1078b802d0a8665b7","tid":240973,"uid":71379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep